response.overview: Rachveli winegrowers will travel to Slovakia to share their experience with the winegrowers of Raci village. Zauri falls in love with a local girl, Darina. He does not give rest. He tries to convince her of love. Soon the Slovaks will pay a return visit to Georgia. Darina, charmed by Georgian hospitality and rachi, who really falls in love with Zauri, finds it difficult to part.
response.title: რაჭა, ჩემო სიყვარულო
